  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Line a baking sheet with parchment paper or aluminum foil.",
    "Place the trout fillets on the prepared baking sheet.",
    "Drizzle the olive oil over the trout fillets.",
    "Sprinkle the minced garlic over the trout fillets.",
    "Sprinkle the chopped oregano, thyme, and parsley over the trout fillets.",
    "Season the trout with salt and black pepper.",
    "Top each trout fillet with crumbled feta cheese and sliced olives.",
    "Bake the trout for 12-15 minutes or until cooked through.",
    "Serve the trout hot with fresh lemon wedges on the side."
